OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVariable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud likely to give a few
OL,7,Fclearer spells overnight. Most of the
OL,8,Fregion becoming largely dry, although
OL,9,Fthere is still a risk of a few showery
OL,10,Foutbreaks of rain. Cloud may thicken
OL,11,Ffrom the west towards dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FTurning breezier Tuesday,
OL,14,Fafter a cloudy morning with showery
OL,15,Frain. Rain dying out and clearing east
OL,16,Fin the afternoon with cloud breaking
OL,17,Fto allow some bright or sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
