OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday, early rain clearing, then
OL,7,Fcolder, brighter with some sunshine.
OL,8,FThursday, windy and bright with
OL,9,Fthickening cloud later. Overnight rain
OL,10,Fclearing Friday morning with sunshine
OL,11,Fand showers. Temperatures near normal.
